import {Nav,Navbar,Container} from 'react-bootstrap'
import {FaRegNewspaper,FaUser} from 'react-icons/fa'

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <header>
        <Navbar bg='dark' variant='dark' expand='lg'>
            <Navbar.Brand>
                SportP
            </Navbar.Brand>
        </Navbar>
    </header>
  )
}

export default Header
